    "Owing to the large amount of pre-training data, supervised learning is expensive in human annotating for these data, so most works focused on self-supervised paradigms, i.e., GL, CL, or HL, to learn general representation capability with low annotation costs.",
    "4) Supervised learning is still used in VFM pre-training.Because the continuity of vision information makes it challenging to separate the semantics of the content [113] only via a self-supervised paradigm.",
